dataset.how_calculated: Sum of gallons of liquid pesticide applications that meet the following qualifications: classified as fungistat, fungicide, fungicide/fungistat, or fungicide/nematicide.  Excludes products classified as disinfectant, sanitizer, microbicide, microbicide/microbistat, insect growth regulator, insecticide, miticide, or termiticide.
dataset.discription: New York State Pesticide Sales and Use Registry (PSUR)
